     <p>Soccer is a sport played globally across different countries by male and female, the young and old and even the youths.</p> 
     <p>Professional soccer is a game played with a simple football by 11 players(10 outfield players and a single goalkeeper) and the game is officiated by 4 officials namely; a referee, an assistant referee, a video assistant referee, and a linesman. </p>
     

        
    
